high_descs: Turn left at the wall and walk forward toward the door.  Turn left at the wall near the door and walk toward the oven.  Walk to the right of the oven.
Pick up the large knife on the counter.
Turn around and face the island counter.
Slice the potato on the island counter.
Turn around and walk toward the counter next to the oven.
Put the knife down on the counter in front of the blue spray bottle.
Turn around and walk toward the island counter.
Grab a slice of potato.
Turn to the right and walk to the counter on the other side of the room.
Open the microwave door, put the potato slice in the microwave, turn on the microwave, open the microwave door, and remove the potato slice.
Walk to the right into the corner of the counter, next to the sink.
Put the potato slice on the top counter in front of the the clear bottle.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato and heat up a slice.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter opposite the stool.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the stove.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter opposite the stool.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Put the potato slice in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the coffee maker.
Put the cooked potato slice on the shelf near the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooked potato on the shelf.

Turn right then face to the island
Slice the potato

Put the knife on the counter

Pick up a slice potato on the island
